        "section_type": "narrative",
        "scope": "series",
        "source_page": 1,
        "source_text": "3M Acrylic Foam Tape GT7100 Series offers very good adhesion performance and high flexibility. These tapes are specifically designed for the attachment of automotive exterior and interior trim applications.",
        "confidence": 0.99
      },
      {
        "section_name": "key_features",
        "section_type": "narrative",
        "scope": "series",
        "source_page": 1,
        "source_text": "Provides final adhesion and holding power to automotive paints and substrates; meets a number of OEM specifications; follows shrinkage and elongation of the plastic part caused by temperature change; good stress relaxation; conforms well to complex geometries; excellent adhesive performance at various temperature conditions; solvent and high temperature resistance.",
        "confidence": 0.96
      },
